Abuja – As the finale of BBNaija ‘Pepper dem’ edition draws closer, Mike’s wife has arrived Nigeria to support her husband. Shakes-Drayton, wife of Big Brother Naija “Pepper Dem” finalist Mike has arrived Nigeria to support her husband in the final week of the show. After spending two months plus without Mike, the joyous wife shared a video of herself and her luggage with the caption, ‘me and my luggage are safe, First time in Nigeria’. Perri Shakes-Drayton Perri, an olympian and tv personality, arrived Lagos on Wednesday night from London. Watch video below: Mike’s wife @itspsd via her instagram story, arrives Nigeria for first time and she’s elated. . #BBNaija #OSGBBNaija #BBNaija2019 A post shared by  Olorisupergal (@olorisupergal) on Oct 3, 2019 at 2:06am PDT Source